              "free_text": [
                "The scanned area was subdivided during the course of",
                "reduction of the experimental data into three",
                "sections of area 9.49, 5.93, and 4.74 cm3. The",
                "average intensity of the primary beam in these",
                "sections was respectively (4.34 + - 0.03)*10**5,",
                " (3.91+ - 0.03)*10**5, and (3.40+ - 0.03) *10**5",
